               <msContents class="#MTM">
                  <summary><p>A collection of 12 medical works, by Akattiyar, entitled <title xml:lang="ta">Vākaṭam</title>. The table of contents (U2) lists only 11 works, whereas Vinson (1868) and Cabaton (1912) list only 10 works. The <title xml:lang="ta">Vaittiyam 50</title> is found twice (U3, f163r and U3, f184r).</p>
<p>The bundle contains the following works in the following order:
<list rend="numbered">
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Irattiṉacurukkam</title> (U3, f1r-f56v).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Ēkamūlicāttiram </title> (U3, f57r-f88v).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Vaittiyam 36</title> (U3, f89r).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Vaittiyam 16</title> (U3, f96r).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Centūram 300</title> (U3, f99r).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Karumacūttiram</title> (U3, f142r).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Vaittiyam 50</title> (U3, f156r).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Muppu 50</title> (U3, f163r).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Cittār Veṇpā 300</title> (U3, f171r).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Vaittiyam Tiraṭṭu 48</title> (U3, f179r).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Vayittiyam 50</title> (U3, f184r).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Nayaṉavitinūl</title> (U3, f191r).</item>
  </list></p>
<p>The usual detached paper sheet that comes with Ducler manuscripts and provides the contents of the bundle is not found or not covered by Gallica photos.</p>
<p>Description based on the digital images available on Gallica.</p>
<p>Dimensions after Cabaton (1912).</p>      </summary>
                  
